Join over 1.4 million Romanians who already use Ghiseul.ro.
No more worries in your interaction with the Romanian public administration!
Use the Ghiseul.ro app to pay online – simply, quickly and securely – over 350 types of public services, fees and taxes, provided by +1200 Romanian institutions and authorities.
All payments made through Ghișeul.ro, the official online payment system of the Romanian Government, have ZERO commission.

Your 7 benefits when using the app:
1. Save time – pay online, with no unnecessary trips to institutions;
2. Non-stop service – pay when you want;
3. ZERO commission on every payment;
4. Safe transactions – the security of transactions is guaranteed and you can check the status of your payments anytime;
5. Payment confirmation issued immediately – you receive the payment confirmation by e-mail, as soon as the transaction is processed;
6. Traceability – see all transactions you made in the Payments History section of the application;
7. Access the proof of payment, which is legally recognized, whenever you need to.

Depending on your needs, you have two options:
1. you create an account using the app, where you will find all payment obligations for taxes;
2. you use the app to make payments that do not require authentication, such as service-specific fees (passport, car licenses, certificates or registration plates, bulletin), fines, court fees, etc.

Create a Ghiseul.ro account using the 7-step Account Creation Guide at: 
https://www.adr.gov.ro/ghiseul-ro/

Don't forget: between January 1 and March 31, you have up to 10% discount on paying taxes.
Terms and conditions apply to this offer. Find out what the specific conditions are from your local town hall.
Also remember that Ghiseul.ro can be used only by Romanian citizens that have a Romanian ID and unique code (CNP) and a bank card.

In 2022, Ghiseul.ro processed over 3.4 million transactions, worth over 1.4 billion lei.
Ghiseul.ro is the official online payment platform of the Romanian state, managed by the Authority for the Digitalization of Romania.

BT Go, your new business banking experience!

BT Go is Banca Transilvania's newest internet and mobile banking solution, which innovatively blends banking and business services in a single ecosystem. BT Go is dedicated exclusively to companies (legal entities and self-employed individuals).
Banca Transilvania is Romania’s market leader in the corporate segment, with over 550,000 active customers.

The new BT Go product covers both the financial-banking needs expected from an internet banking application and the management needs of any business:
Your company accounts and transactions are always at your fingertips
-	Quickly view all your BT accounts, open new accounts, and close a current account directly from the app;
-	Rename and reorder accounts and bookmark your favorite;
-	Identify and check transactions and their status through a multitude of search filters;
-	Generate and download monthly or daily account statements;
-	Download the list of transactions in CSV format and have your statements available in MT940 format;
-	Download monthly statements for your accounts in the last 10 years, all in one convenient ZIP file;
-	View all the company cards, issue new cards, block them or change transaction limits;
-	Reissue the PIN code for a card directly from the app;
-	Open classic and negotiated deposits and quickly open savings accounts;
-	Access your loan details, quickly download your repayment schedule, or prepay active loans;
-	View and trade fund units in your BT Asset Management investment portfolio;
-	Enjoy access to Open Banking under the Payment Services Directive II (PSD2).

Quick and easy payments
-	Make payments between your own accounts or to your partners, in any currency;
-	Create payment packages or upload payment files for simultaneous signing;
-	Create payments that require multiple signatures or receive payments created by other users for signing;
-	Quickly perform classic or negotiated foreign exchange operations;
-	Schedule payments for a future date or set up recurring payments;
-	Add, remove, and manage your partners' details;
-	Import payroll files.

Your bills right in your banking app
-	Issue, reverse, cancel, set recurrences and customize invoices directly from the BT Go app (through integration with the FGO billing app). This gives you simple, fast and free access to the benefits of a dedicated billing solution directly in BT Go;
-	e-Factura - log in to your SPV account, send your invoices automatically and track the processing by ANAF. Additionally, view all the invoices received via SPV in the app;
-	Pay incoming invoices quickly, while also enjoying multiple payment functionalities - select and send up to 5 invoices for payment at once;
-	Invoices are automatically linked to payments and collections, so you always have an up-to-date overview of your finances;
-	Download invoices directly from the banking app whenever you need and send them to your customers.

Intuitive and user-friendly dashboard
-	Enjoy direct access to your accounts and the FGO billing solution;
-	Quickly make transfers of any kind;
-	View the balance of your favorite account and the most recent transactions and compare payments with collections over the last 4 months;
-	Quick access to your deposits, loans and cards;
-      View incoming notifications in the Notification Center;
-      If you have POS, ePOS and/or eCommerce, you have access to details, graphs and lists of transactions, collection reports.
